{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1261,"text":"Five years ago, I experienced a bit"},{"time":3783,"text":"of what it must have been like to be Alice in Wonderland."},{"time":7119,"text":"Penn State asked me, a communications teacher,"},{"time":9782,"text":"to teach a communications class for engineering students."},{"time":13122,"text":"And I was scared. (Laughter)"},{"time":15728,"text":"Really scared. Scared of these students with their big brains"},{"time":19399,"text":"and their big books and their big, unfamiliar words."},{"time":23106,"text":"But as these conversations unfolded,"},{"time":26311,"text":"I experienced what Alice must have when she went down"},{"time":29219,"text":"that rabbit hole and saw that door to a whole new world."},{"time":33396,"text":"That's just how I felt as I had those conversations"},{"time":36007,"text":"with the students. I was amazed at the ideas"},{"time":38756,"text":"that they had, and I wanted others to experience this wonderland as well."},{"time":43722,"text":"And I believe the key to opening that door"},{"time":46353,"text":"is great communication."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47643,"text":"We desperately need great communication from our"},{"time":50527,"text":"scientists and engineers in order to change the world."},{"time":53586,"text":"Our scientists and engineers are the ones"},{"time":56476,"text":"that are tackling our grandest challenges, from energy"},{"time":59642,"text":"to environment to health care, among others,"},{"time":62647,"text":"and if we don't know about it and understand it,"},{"time":65809,"text":"then the work isn't done, and I believe it's our responsibility"},{"time":68817,"text":"as non-scientists to have these interactions."},{"time":71768,"text":"But these great conversations can't occur if our scientists"},{"time":74928,"text":"and engineers don't invite us in to see their wonderland."},{"time":78162,"text":"So scientists and engineers, please, talk nerdy to us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":83641,"text":"I want to share a few keys on how you can do that"},{"time":86128,"text":"to make sure that we can see that your science is sexy"},{"time":90203,"text":"and that your engineering is engaging."},{"time":92803,"text":"First question to answer for us: so what?"},{"time":96536,"text":"Tell us why your science is relevant to us."},{"time":100491,"text":"Don't just tell me that you study trabeculae,"},{"time":103121,"text":"but tell me that you study trabeculae, which is the mesh-like structure of our bones"},{"time":107018,"text":"because it's important to understanding and treating osteoporosis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111631,"text":"And when you're describing your science, beware of jargon."},{"time":116137,"text":"Jargon is a barrier to our understanding of your ideas."},{"time":120013,"text":"Sure, you can say \"spatial and temporal,\" but why not just say"},{"time":123089,"text":"\"space and time,\" which is so much more accessible to us?"},{"time":126515,"text":"And making your ideas accessible is not the same as dumbing it down."},{"time":131663,"text":"Instead, as Einstein said, make everything"},{"time":134440,"text":"as simple as possible, but no simpler."},{"time":137874,"text":"You can clearly communicate your science"},{"time":140647,"text":"without compromising the ideas."},{"time":143334,"text":"A few things to consider are having examples, stories"},{"time":147279,"text":"and analogies. Those are ways to engage"},{"time":148984,"text":"and excite us about your content."},{"time":151166,"text":"And when presenting your work, drop the bullet points."},{"time":157479,"text":"Have you ever wondered why they're called bullet points? (Laughter)"},{"time":161332,"text":"What do bullets do? Bullets kill,"},{"time":163700,"text":"and they will kill your presentation."},{"time":166012,"text":"A slide like this is not only boring, but it relies too much"},{"time":170191,"text":"on the language area of our brain, and causes us to become overwhelmed."},{"time":173918,"text":"Instead, this example slide by Genevieve Brown is"},{"time":177822,"text":"much more effective. It's showing that the special structure"},{"time":180704,"text":"of trabeculae are so strong that they actually inspired"},{"time":184368,"text":"the unique design of the Eiffel Tower."},{"time":187223,"text":"And the trick here is to use a single, readable sentence"},{"time":190903,"text":"that the audience can key into if they get a bit lost,"},{"time":193955,"text":"and then provide visuals which appeal to our other senses"},{"time":197233,"text":"and create a deeper sense of understanding"},{"time":199647,"text":"of what's being described."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201286,"text":"So I think these are just a few keys that can help"},{"time":204136,"text":"the rest of us to open that door and see the wonderland"},{"time":207658,"text":"that is science and engineering."},{"time":209874,"text":"And because the engineers that I've worked with have"},{"time":212323,"text":"taught me to become really in touch with my inner nerd,"},{"time":216123,"text":"I want to summarize with an equation. (Laughter)"},{"time":219076,"text":"Take your science, subtract your bullet points"},{"time":223321,"text":"and your jargon, divide by relevance,"},{"time":226099,"text":"meaning share what's relevant to the audience,"},{"time":228546,"text":"and multiply it by the passion that you have for"},{"time":231337,"text":"this incredible work that you're doing,"},{"time":233560,"text":"and that is going to equal incredible interactions"},{"time":236338,"text":"that are full of understanding."},{"time":238812,"text":"And so, scientists and engineers, when you've solved"},{"time":242274,"text":"this equation, by all means, talk nerdy to me. (Laughter)"},{"time":247370,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}